videos.headline: UConn turns defense into offense on Nika Muhl's dime
videos.description: Dorka Juhasz comes up with a steal, then Nika Muhl throws a pinpoint pass ahead for a UConn basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn turns defense into offense on Nika Muhl's dime) 2022/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Azzi Fudd scores after pickpocket steal
videos.description: Azzi Fudd gets an easy layup in transition after stealing the ball away on defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Azzi Fudd scores after pickpocket steal) 2022/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caroline Ducharme beats first-half buzzer for UConn
videos.description: UConn takes a five-point lead into the half as Caroline Ducharme lays it in to beat the buzzer against Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caroline Ducharme beats first-half buzzer for UConn) 2022/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sonya Morris swishes home 3 for Texas
videos.description: Texas pulls within 10 against UConn as Sonya Morris buries a 3 with a hand in her face.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sonya Morris swishes home 3 for Texas) 2022/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Azzi Fudd drops defender, splashes jumper for UConn
